Archer's Revenge is an action masala novella giving you the experience of eating
a home cooked meal. As you savour the nostalgia, and recollect the familiar
places, he never forgets to add a few surprises that make you both laugh and
cry.

Destination Infinity in this debut novel inspires every one of us that we too
can write. All it takes is a healthy dose of foolhardiness.

Enjoy it with your kids and the kid in you.